<br>
Trak is a good idea, as he is already done with smaller entourages frequently.  If you can find him up and get a MT/healer to hold agro would be cake for a small force of crazy magi.  Of course having mages on when hes up is another issue.  Doing the umbral cycle is another idea.<br>
<br>
May want to consider doing a flag run too, something like grummas or poi dragon for factory.  They would require a small contingent of non-mages but certinaly in both cases having 20-30 mages on hand would basically garuntee you had the dps for it.<br>
<br>
